'''美国联邦人事管理局'''（{{lang-en|United States Office of Personnel Management}}，简称{{lang|en|'''OPM'''}}）是[[美国联邦政府|美国联邦政府]]负责管理[[美国联邦公务员|公务人员]]的[[美国政府独立机构|独立机构]]。该局拟定联邦人力资源政策，监督、支持联邦政府雇员、退休人员及其家属的{{le|联邦雇员健康福利项目|Federal Employees Health Benefits Program|医疗保健}}（FEHB）、{{le|联邦雇员团体人寿保险法案|Federal Employees' Group Life Insurance Act|人寿保险}}（FEGLI）以及退休福利（{{le|公务员退休制度|Civil Service Retirement System}} CSRS / FERS，但不包括{{le|节俭储蓄计划|Thrift Savings Plan}} TSP）。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.opm.gov/about-us/our-mission-role-history/what-we-do/ |title=Our Mission, Role & History – What We Do |publisher=U.S. Office of Personnel Management |location=Washington, D.C. |accessdate=24 January 2018 |archive-date=2021-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423005428/https://www.opm.gov/about-us/our-mission-role-history/what-we-do/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

该局由局长领导，局长由[[美国总统|总统]]提名并由[[美国参议院|参议院]]确认。该局现无正任局长，由迈克尔·里加代理局长职务。

==历史==
1883年，[[彭德尔顿法案|彭德尔顿法案]]成立{{le|美国联邦公务员委员会|nited States Civil Service Commission}}。1979年1月1日，该委员会被撤销，联邦人事管理局取而代之，法源为{{le|1978年公务员改革法案|Civil Service Reform Act of 1978}}和1978年第2号重组计划 ({{USFedReg|43|36037}}, {{USStat|92|3783}})。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.opm.gov/glossary/|title=Glossary of Terms|publisher=|accessdate=5 January 2016|archive-date=2013-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130117163746/http://www.opm.gov/glossary/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1996年，本局的搜索部门被私有化，并成立了[[美国新闻署|美国新闻署]]。<ref name=Gayathri>Gayathri, Amrutha. "[http://www.ibtimes.com/usis-vetted-snowden-under-investigation-booz-allen-hamilton-overlooked-snowden-resume-discrepancies USIS That Vetted Snowden Under Investigation; Booz Allen Hamilton Overlooked Snowden Resume Discrepancies] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/usis-vetted-snowden-under-investigation-booz-allen-hamilton-overlooked-snowden-resume-discrepancies |date=20200919205708 }}." ''[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]''. June 21, 2013. Retrieved on July 1, 2013.</ref>

==功能==
根据其官方网站，人事管理局的任务是“招募、保有和表彰为美国人民服务的世界一流队伍”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.opm.gov/BiographyofAnIdeal/SubMain1979-present.asp|title=Biography of an Ideal|publisher=|accessdate=5 January 2016|archive-date=2012-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120305051034/http://www.opm.gov/BiographyofAnIdeal/SubMain1979-present.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref> 本局负责维护行政法体系中的独立性和中立性。从技术上来说，{{le|行政法法官|Administrative law judge}}（或称听证官）由本局独家雇用，从而实际上消除了其他机构的任何自由裁量雇用程序。在1978年《公务员改革法案》中，重申了联邦行政程序法中禁止对行政法法官进行绩效评估的规定，将行政法法官排除于适用绩效评估的“雇员”概念之外，以维护“目前为行政法法官提供保护的系统”。行政法法官的分级和薪资水平，也由人事管理局确定。每有行政法法官出缺，本局使用严格的选拔流程拟出三个候选人名单，然后从这些候选人中决定，通常优先考虑退伍军人。

人事管理局还负责美国政府{{le|安全审查|Security clearance}}的大部分管理工作（{{le|国家背景调查局|National Background Investigations Bureau}}进行了这些调查）。各行政部门单独的安全过关标准被整合成一个全政府通用标准，[[美国核能管理委员会|美国核能管理委员会]]仍保留单独标准。人事管理局负责调查个人，以给予他们机密和绝密密级许可。<ref>{{cite web|title=Audit of the Federal Investigations Servies' Case Review Process Over Background Investigations|url=http://www.opm.gov/our-inspector-general/reports/2014/audit-of-the-federal-investigative-services-case-review-process-over-background-investigations.pdf|location=page 2|website=opm.gov|accessdate=6 June 2014|archive-date=2018-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181209120207/https://www.opm.gov/our-inspector-general/reports/2014/audit-of-the-federal-investigative-services-case-review-process-over-background-investigations.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> 但{{le|敏感分割信息|Sensitive Compartmented Information}}仍由特定机构管理。

人事管理局还负责公务员退休制度(FERS\CSRS)雇员的退休申请。<ref>{{cite web |author=7 MAR |url=https://www.opm.gov/Blogs/Retire/ |title=Retirement Info Center |publisher=Opm.gov |date= |accessdate=2019-06-19 |archive-date=2021-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430223633/https://www.opm.gov/Blogs/Retire/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 本局对联邦雇员全勤<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.opm.gov/retirement-services/publications-forms/pamphlets/sf3113.pdf |title=Pamphlet |website=opm.gov |format=PDF |access-date=2019-06-18 |archive-date=2021-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318235825/https://www.opm.gov/retirement-services/publications-forms/pamphlets/sf3113.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>和残疾退休案做出决定。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://federalemployeelawblog.com/2016/12/10/opm-disability-retirement/|title=OPM Disability Retirement|first=|last=berrylegal|date=December 11, 2016|website=Federal Employee Law Blog|access-date=2020-09-26|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127222328/https://federalemployeelawblog.com/2016/12/10/opm-disability-retirement/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 本局还监督联邦雇员健康福利项目(FEHB)和人寿保险(FEGLI)，联邦雇员的健康保险和人寿保险计划。但是，本局并不监督节俭储蓄计划(TSP)，TSP由另一联邦独立机构[[美国联邦退休储蓄投资委员会|美国联邦退休储蓄投资委员会]]处理。

==周转基金==
人事管理局周转基金被称为其“服务费”业务，它将联邦预算资金从各个联邦机构转移到本局人力资源（HR）服务。在2002–12年的10年中，该基金的资金增长了两倍。<ref>[http://www.avuetech.com/2013/09/24/opm-fact-sheet/ Fact Sheet: OPM Revolving Fund, Products and Services] {{Wayback|url=http://www.avuetech.com/2013/09/24/opm-fact-sheet/ |date=20140224005601 }}. Avue Technologies Corporation. 2013-09-24 (Retrieved 2014-02-17)</ref> 该基金值金额有20亿美元，几乎等于人事管理局预算的全部（占到90％）。<ref>Reilly, Sean. [http://www.federaltimes.com/article/20140213/MGMT/302130008/OPM-inspector-general-getting-more-money-revolving-fund-oversight "OPM inspector general getting more money for revolving fund oversight”]. ''Federal Times''. 2014-02-13 (Retrieved 2014-02-17)</ref>

2013年7月，共和党得克萨斯州联邦众议员[[布雷克·法蘭索德|布雷克·法蘭索德]]主导通过了《人事管理局监察长办公室法案》。<ref>[https://www.govtrack.us/congress/bills/113/hr2860 "OPM IG Act (H.R. 2860)”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.govtrack.us/congress/bills/113/hr2860 |date=20210228012621 }}. GovTrack.us. (2014) (Retrieved 2014-02-17)</ref> 该法案将加强对基金的监督。 法蘭索德提出该法案是为了回应欺诈指控和表达对安全审查背景调查的担忧。<ref name="ripadv">[http://riponadvance.com/news/opm-inspector-general-act-signed-law/6615 "OPM Inspector General Act signed into law”]. ''Ripon Advance''. 2014-02-17 (Retrieved 2014-02-17)</ref> 该法案规定将由周转基金来支持调查、监督活动和审计的开支。<ref name="this week">[http://theweekincongress.com/2014/01/16/h-r-2860-opm-ig-act/ "H.R.2860 OPM IG Act”] {{Wayback|url=http://theweekincongress.com/2014/01/16/h-r-2860-opm-ig-act/ |date=20200121133706 }} ''The Week in Congress''; Volume 10 Number 3. 2014-01-17 (Retrieved 2014-02-17)</ref> 2014年2月，[[奥巴马|奥巴马]]总统签署了该法案，使成为法律。<ref>Carney, Jay (White House Press Secretary). [http://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2014/02/12/statement-press-secretary-hr-2860-s-1901 "Statement by the Press Secretary on H.R. 2860, S. 1901”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2014/02/12/statement-press-secretary-hr-2860-s-1901 |date=20161209103333 }}. The White House, Office of the Press Secretary. 2014-02-12 (Retrieved 2014-02-17)</ref>

该基金的历史可以追溯到1980年代初，当时被用于两项主要活动：对政府人员的培训和背景调查。<ref>U.S. Government Accountability Office. [http://www.gao.gov/products/GAO/GGD-84-23 "OPM's Revolving Fund Policy Should Be Clarified and Management Controls Strengthened”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gao.gov/products/GAO/GGD-84-23 |date=20201202002633 }}. GGD-84-23: Published: Oct 13, 1983. Publicly Released: Oct 13, 1983 (Retrieved 2014-02-17)</ref>

